<ol>
<li><%= link_to "Creating a gem that works on both Rails 3.0.x and Rails 3.1.x", "http://rwilcox.tumblr.com/post/8920453306/creating-a-gem-that-works-on-both-rails-3-0-x-and-rails" -%></li>
<li><%= link_to "SASS variables and the Rails 3.1 asset pipeline", "http://rwilcox.tumblr.com/post/9038701675/sass-variables-and-the-rails-3-1-asset-pipeline" -%></li>
</ol>

